    public class RadixRangeSearch2d.RadixGridRatioComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<com.solace.aaron.geo.api.RadixRangeSearch2d.RadixGrid>
    This internal helper class is used to sort the various grids to determine which should be split next. There are a number of different ways to sort/weight the grid squares, and by varying the algorithm it will change which grids will be split first.
